{"tid":1131080,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《復仇者聯盟 4: 終局之戰》刷新香港首周票房紀錄","createTime":"2019-04-29T12:39:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T13:33:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"677f134d42fc38323b6088da8f0dd8b44f256611","tid":1131080,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T12:39:04.000Z","msg":"復仇者聯盟 4: 終局之戰》(Avengers: Endgame)於 2019 年 4 月 24 日開畫，至 2019 年 4 月 28 日上映僅五天票房高達港幣$96,288,283，打破過往紀錄。且截至今日(29日)下午 3 時止，總收入為港幣$102,752,845，成為香港歷年首周票房破億元之影片；之前首周票房最高紀錄是由《復仇者聯盟 3: 無限之戰》於 2018 年所創，當時首周收入為港幣$86,134,777。<br />\n<br />\n  《復仇者聯盟 4: 終局之戰》屢創新高，27 日打破自己於24 日所創下的最高單日票房，首五天每天都打破歷年單日最高票房收入。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/2019/0429/U634P22DT20190429184924.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2019%2F0429%2FU634P22DT20190429184924.jpg&h=9d6a5796&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f7df60ded33b575ca23fcc7d57eddbae99a8e6c","tid":1131080,"uid":146949,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T13:02:56.000Z","msg":"只有marvel超越到marvel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3171ca0b89fba96d927545046234cb96a8ac6b1","tid":1131080,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T13:03:45.000Z","msg":"復仇者聯盟1呢"},{"pid":"f580f47d79a0efe574d2405229d347445b27159e","tid":1131080,"uid":110196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T13:20:36.000Z","msg":"其實睇既人數應該冇乜點升<br />\n只係戲飛加價"},{"pid":"7851f0937ebd21df44d4782c72b7f1c7621259fa","tid":1131080,"uid":56544,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T13:33:30.000Z","msg":"共通點係全部都有rdj<br />\n所以實在有少少為marvel未來擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}